description: Returns the webhook information that corresponds to a specified webhook ID.

parameters.name: webhookId
parameters.description: The unique ID for a webhook.

nested_items.name: webhookArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the webhook.

nested_items.name: appId
nested_items.description: The unique ID of an Amplify app.

nested_items.name: branchName
nested_items.description: The name for a branch that is part of an Amplify app.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: A timestamp of when Amplify created the webhook in your Git repository.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: A timestamp of when Amplify updated the webhook in your Git repository.
